lead_paragraph: Arsene Wenger is the right manager to lead Arsenal forward, the club's chief executive Ivan Gazidis has said, despite doubts over the Frenchman's contract at the Premier League club.

headline.print_headline: CEO Gazidis Backs Wenger to Deliver Success at Arsenal
headline.main: CEO Gazidis Backs Wenger to Deliver Success at Arsenal
